395
00:18:11,548 --> 00:18:13,088
The lighthouse keeper.

396
00:18:13,175 --> 00:18:16,345
The loneliest man in the world.

397
00:18:16,428 --> 00:18:17,848
He'll understand me.

398
00:18:22,518 --> 00:18:23,438
(panting)

399
00:18:26,563 --> 00:18:27,613
Earl.

400
00:18:27,689 --> 00:18:29,649
My new friend's name is Earl.

401
00:18:29,733 --> 00:18:31,613
Here I come, buddy!

402
00:18:31,693 --> 00:18:34,323
No more loneliness
for Homer and Earl.

403
00:18:37,908 --> 00:18:39,868
A machine?

404
00:18:39,952 --> 00:18:42,252
Earl's a machine?

405
00:18:42,329 --> 00:18:45,619
Oh, that's just perfect.

406
00:18:45,707 --> 00:18:49,247
Homer's desperate search
for a soul mate has yielded

407
00:18:49,336 --> 00:18:51,506
a lighthouse-keeping robot.

408
00:18:51,588 --> 00:18:53,128
Oh, wow.

409
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:56,510
Hey, look, is that Dad?

410
00:18:56,593 --> 00:18:59,643
Either that or Batman's
really let himself go.

411
00:18:59,721 --> 00:19:01,521
Alone.

412
00:19:01,598 --> 00:19:03,098
Oh, I'm alone.

413
00:19:03,183 --> 00:19:05,313
I'm a lonely,
insignificant speck

414
00:19:05,394 --> 00:19:08,814
