goodness you're safe.

433
00:19:52,608 --> 00:19:54,108
-Marge?
-I woke up,

434
00:19:54,193 --> 00:19:56,323
and you weren't there,
and I was so worried.

435
00:19:56,403 --> 00:19:57,913
Really? You were?

436
00:19:57,988 --> 00:20:00,278
But how did you find me?

437
00:20:00,365 --> 00:20:02,905
Well... I was sure
you'd be on foot

438
00:20:02,993 --> 00:20:04,243
because you always say

439
00:20:04,328 --> 00:20:06,748
